{"tid":2249648,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方偷步解封證物查閱兼檢取與案無關物品 《蘋果》要求法庭頒令禁制","createTime":"2020-10-19T12:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T15:38:31.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b95ff0fe41ea624234a0bac664e04845ec6c05d1","tid":2249648,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T12:59:15.000Z","msg":"警方今年8月大肆搜查將軍澳《蘋果日報》大樓，以牽涉國安法罪行和詐騙案為由檢走大批物件。壹傳媒早前入稟高等法院，要求取回新聞材料與涉及法律專業保密權的資料。惟壹傳媒其後得悉，原來警方在法庭未指示如何鑑定上述資料前，竟已開始檢閱內容，而且警方更利用國安法手令，檢取與國安法罪行無關的物品。《蘋果》今要求法庭頒令警方交回搜查令範圍以外的文件及資料。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》總編輯羅偉光表示，要求法庭頒令，是希望警方交回搜查令範圍以外的文件及資料，對於警方在未獲法庭頒令前，偷步解封證物查閱，令人無法接受，感到極度憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/U4RAZ3TTO5C7HHQI3R6C7I7CJU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FU4RAZ3TTO5C7HHQI3R6C7I7CJU%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZojkqoP0ISDA%2F8fQ3RVu%2FF4%3D&h=16970dcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FU4RAZ3TTO5C7HHQI3R6C7I7CJU%2F&h=f448d6fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/U4RAZ3TTO5C7HHQI3R6C7I7CJU/</a>"},{"pid":"4b7ec91cb31b26e7380298e2a96e1dd4979c42dc","tid":2249648,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4944fcbbffa275a5cbf92bbf41422b16ee1710d4","tid":2249648,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:01:20.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"b64ee4a6520ee465edb8c841035d6610d3f88467","tid":2249648,"uid":258974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:05:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src